===Noun===
'''poof''' (''plural:'' '''[[poofs]]''' ''or (jocularly)'' '''[[pooves]]''')

# (''derogatory'') A male [[homosexual]], especially one who is [[effeminate]].
# The product of flatulence, or the sound of breaking wind.

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|poof||}}

# To vanish or disappear.
#: '''''Poof''', he was gone.''
# To break wind; to [[fart]].

